FBIS3-10945 "drlat050_o_94017" FBIS-LAT-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 Colombia Correction to Banco Latino Scandal PA1003153594 PA1003153594 Article Type:BFN The following correction pertains to the item headlined "Venezuela's Banco Latino Scandal Reaches Colombia," published in the 10 March Latin America DAILY REPORT, page 40. Column one, paragraph four, first sentence make read: ...are in Colombia. Lermi Mendoza -- the mastermind behind all of the legal machinations to obtain unsecured loans, loans obtained by way of false documents, and all operations carried out by front men -- is in Colombia, along with his wife... (rewording sentence)
